title: Ep 45: The Inner Gremlin
description: You'd better watch out or that inner gremlin will get you. Who is that self loathing turd inside of all of us and how do we stop it from ruining our lives?  Woody Allen's obsession with young girls. Also, we do some positive affirmations.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
